{"word":"G4650 - σκορπίζω - skorpízō - skor-pid'-zo - Disperse abroad","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκορπίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>skorpízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>skor-pid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Disperse abroad"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிதறடி, வாரியிறை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to scatter"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Apparently from the same as <a href=\"#/G4651 - σκορπίος - skorpíos - skor-pee'-os/4651\">G4651</a> (through the idea of <i>penetrating</i>); to <i>dissipate</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>put to flight</i>, <i>waste</i>, <i>be liberal:</i> - disperse abroad, scatter (abroad)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1287 - διασκορπίζω - diaskorpízō - dee-as-kor-pid'-zo/1287\">G1287</a>, <a href=\"#/G4650 - σκορπίζω - skorpízō - skor-pid'-zo/4650\">G4650</a>"}]}